  "apiSuggestion": {
    "endpoint": "GET /api/user-growth/account-performance",
    "query": {
      "source": "渠道筛选（tiktok/facebook/google 或空=全部）",
      "platform": "应用筛选（应用名或应用ID，空=全部）",
      "ownerId": "负责人 ID（可选，空=全部）",
      "dateStart": "开始日期（YYYY-MM-DD）",
      "dateEnd": "结束日期（YYYY-MM-DD）",
      "kw": "搜索关键字（可选，用于账户名筛选；也可前端本地过滤）"
    },
    "response": "直接返回 sampleResponse 结构",
    "enumSuggestion": {
      "tableRow.status": ["normal", "warning", "roi_low"],
      "alertItem.type": ["over_budget", "low_roi", "low_usage", "insufficient_balance", "roi_drop"]
    },
    "notes": [
      "当前前端把 spend/budget/cpi/installs/roi* 都当作数值渲染；KPI.value 则为已格式化的字符串。",
      "如果后端希望 KPI 也返回原始数值，可扩展字段（例如 rawValue/units），前端再格式化。"
    ]
  }
